metadata.name: BananaMama
metadata.description:
I present project “GIF me your fantasy” through a card game, where the assembled deck of cards represents the fantasies of people surrounding me. Having reimagined the plots, the images and the symbols, I created the new “decorations”, where with the phantasmagoric characters you can risk without risking, express desire without shame, be dependent without being dependent, take yours without fearing to cause pain.
Welcome to the erotic intelligence, 

Pull your card!
